  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, I don't know what it was, because for days before that, people were all sewing all sorts of rucksack-type things that they could and, and suitcases and, and bags and sacks to squeeze in whatever they thought would help them to save themselves.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whatever they thought they would need or could use, not, of course, realizing that that was really part of the-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] of the German way of lulling people into believing that there was something beyond what was, and maybe even better.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a, a really elementary kind of psychology that they practiced, which was so useful to them in cowing the population that was to become the subject of their murder, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a human psychology such that you will not only cling to any kind of hope, but create elaborate scenarios for how it is going to be better even than it is, let alone not worse.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The notion when they tell you that you have to pack, I don't know, 50 kilograms of-- and a week-long food for the trip, it, it makes you think that there is a trip, that you'll be traveling, that you will be eating, that, that you will change your clothes, and that there will be a toilet or, or-- it, it, it makes you think that there will be a, perhaps a, a, an inconvenience, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but not utter and complete devastation.",
      "word_count": 85
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "East.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The word was always east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Evacuation to the east, where all the Jews may have been brought together, where the enemy isn't going to reach us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After all, we were in real danger, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians may come any minute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what could be worse than that?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
